  <div class="columns small-12 medium-8 mar-b-30">
    <h2>Completing the Outcome Measures</h2>
    <p>Please note you are welcome to complete Outcome Measures Online before your session.</p>
    <h4>When should I complete the Measure?</h4>
    <p>Before every session, as close to the session as is practical (e.g. completing the measure the night before your appointment would be fine).</p>
    <h4>How do I complete the Outcome Measure?</h4>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="columns small-2 medium-1">
        <span class="tt-dropcap-round">1</span>
      </div>
      <div class="columns small-10 medium-11 mar-b-30">
        <p>Visit the <a href="https://www.oqanalyst.com/LilleyPlace/kiosk/" target="_blank">OQ Analyst Kiosk Login</a> page</p>
        <img class="" title="OQ1" src="http://lilleyplace/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Outcome-Measure_Q1.jpg" width="626" height="417" alt="OQ1">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="columns small-12 mar-b-30">
        <p class="small"><em>Important:</em> Date of Birth should be entered in the Australian format not the USA format. Enter as (DD/MM/YYYY) ‚Äì not the way listed on the log in page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="columns small-2 medium-1">
        <span class="tt-dropcap-round">2</span>
      </div>
      <div class="columns small-10 medium-11 mar-b-30">
        <img class="" title="OQ2" src="http://lilleyplace/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Outcome-Measure_Q2.jpg" width="626" height="417" alt="OQ2">
      </div>
    </div>
    <h4>Which measure (Instrument) should I select?</h4>
    <p><strong>Adults</strong> please select: OQ¬Æ-45.2<br>
    <strong>Children</strong> and <strong>Young People</strong> (aged between 12-17 years) select : YOQ¬Æ‚Äì2.0-SR<br>
    Parents/Carers of a Child or Young Person (aged 4-17 years) select : YOQ¬Æ‚Äì2.0<br>
    Setting of Care should be set to: ‚ÄúOutpatient‚Äù<br>
    Clinic should be set to: <em>‚ÄúLilley Place‚Äù</em></p>
    <p>Once you have completed all the questions on the measure and pressed the submit button, all information will be sent to Lilley Place Clinical Psychology, and your therapist will have access to this for your upcoming session.</p>
  </div>
